{"tid":370894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杏花邨停車場水浸傳有三人失蹤 蛙人到場","createTime":"2017-08-23T09:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T10:51:32.000Z","uid":89134,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"305d88e4bb67c69fa810d40d72e3263b56eea687","tid":370894,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:52:02.000Z","msg":"現場消息指，水淹停車場事件，一度傳出有3人失蹤，被困在車場內，消防蛙人亦到場搜救，最新消息指3人已全數尋回。<br />\n<br />\n杏花邨俱樂部停車場被水淹浸，逾30輛車頓變「潛水艇」，管理公司雖然曾嘗試用細泵泵水，但不成功，消防亦未能幫忙解決，管理公司為加快處理情況，決定召大型泵車到場，泵車於下午4時許到達涉事停車場。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有車主憶述事發時驚險一幕。女車主方太表示，她的朋友住在停車場附近，見到開始有水浸情況，即時致電通知她把車駛走，她本來「懶得落樓，但諗諗吓都係落樓睇下」，一到停車場，發現水位已浸至腳眼，她及時將車駛走，同時通知朋友謝先生將車駛走，她質疑管理公司未有做好防風措施。<br />\n<br />\n而其友人謝先生指，接到通知後10分鐘已趕到停車場，當時已水浸及大脾，因水浸關後，車門未能打開，他在慌亂之際，見海水洶湧地不斷沿鈄路湧落停車場，他擔心會沒頂浸死，於是決定棄車逃生，他逃離車場後不久，車場已被水完全淹浸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最新消息唔知真定假<br />\n三個人係咪見到老婆浸死係停車場諗住就此輕生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbef9739cc10e0337a6eb3f073263758f639e918","tid":370894,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98ca01ffd06fd59a87b7d44f48d7b972b5b05be5","tid":370894,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:54:10.000Z","msg":"老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228d60825ce92517a2be6b024826c49b42de4154","tid":370894,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係近廿年首次風暴死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得有人失蹤係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為啲水湧得咁快<br />\n真係好危險 會死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過尋回聽落好似有啲流<br />\n同埋冇講係咪有生命危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36a1da456ad7d03026e0bf1c2c4b36a168fd8c0","tid":370894,"uid":81045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"佢哋講嘅尋回係指喺其他地方搵返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5529f470742efb3e5dfab8404f2721c0f40b894f","tid":370894,"uid":2247,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我唔撚個浸左成個下午先知有人<br />\n9 成係想惜消防鬼部泵車抽水啦"},{"pid":"fb474e4baab93629a1a7f06e1d8e9ea1bc6167e9","tid":370894,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母我唔撚信浸左成個下午先知有人<br />\n9 成係想借消防鬼部泵車抽水啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e97c160b37dd81c2b74be67d0310421a6fbd4a8a","tid":370894,"uid":953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母我唔撚個浸左成個下午先知有人<br />\n9 成係想惜消防鬼部泵車抽水啦</blockquote><br />\n點泵都無用啦， 啲車全部total loss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fd7dddad41615e942691bfc7bd48d6d819d3cc","tid":370894,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:19:27.000Z","msg":"生前有冇借錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40846af194f5709a1ba9a69676285956f812c6ab","tid":370894,"uid":18416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:19:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母我唔撚信浸左成個下午先知有人<br />\n9 成係想借消防鬼部泵車抽水啦</blockquote></blockquote><br />\nbrother 心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8d3f7281fd67334596f2ccfecbaa12e14ac59e","tid":370894,"u